query:
INSERT INTO building_codes (code, title, edition, jurisdiction, year, pageCount, isActive) VALUES
('NBC_2020', 'National Building Code of Canada 2020', '2020 Edition', 'Canada', 2020, 1528, 1),
('BCBC_2024', 'British Columbia Building Code 2024', '2024 Edition, Revision 1', 'British Columbia', 2024, 1906, 1),
('NBC_2023_AB', 'National Building Code – 2023 Alberta Edition', '2023 Alberta Edition', 'Alberta', 2023, 1570, 1)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
  title = VALUES(title),
  edition = VALUES(edition),
  jurisdiction = VALUES(jurisdiction),
  year = VALUES(year),
  pageCount = VALUES(pageCount);
